 such as LED bulbs, LED battens, emergency LEDs, LED panels, LED downlights and spotlights, and outdoor and festive lighting; professional lighting, including indoor architectural, commercial, industrial, facade, and flood lighting; electrical accessories comprising surge protectors, extension reels, multi-plugs, doorbells, plug tops, immersion heaters, and dry irons; and mosquito racquets. In addition, the company is involved in distribution of electrical products; and trading of raw materials. It sells its products under the Eveready, PowerCell, Ultima, Shakti, and Uniross brands. Eveready Industries India Limited was founded in 1905 and is based in Kolkata, India."}}